title: Palo Alto Battlefield National Historical Park: Photo Gallery
body: Photo Gallery       Palo Alto Battlefield is pleased to offer these images. The following photos are in the public domain and may be reprinted free of charge with appropriate credit. Photo credit should be given to the NPS and/or to the photographer. Additional photos will be added over time so check back often.  Â                 Scenic Views   30 Photos  While Palo Alto is a battle site, the park is also home to a wealth of natural beauty.          Living History   84 Photos  The park offers living history programs from September through May. Check with the front desk for the latest program schedule.          Events & Programs   66 Photos  Palo Alto offers special events and programs throughout the year. Contact the park for the latest special event and program schedule.            Nature   52 Photos  Although known for the battle that took place here, Palo Alto offers a wealth of natural resources.
